{"tid":1467282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尊重前線 團結才是力量","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:22:08.000Z","uid":155584,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"148fbc4403daa2717987f35673fb4cfaee8576c2","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"係唔係一直要班前線<strong>打生打死</strong>，一直<strong>冒俾人拉嘅風險</strong> 一路等你地去爭取所謂嘅民意，民意呢樣野由雨革講到而家，係啊係重要但我覺得今次事件雖然損失左少部分民意（可能啦因為仲未知聽日會點），不過更重要係我地打擊到對家手段，而家起碼叫有反制手段，捉鬼好成功，又keep到<strong>不分化不割席</strong>，同埋起碼勇武班手足因為今次可以暫時平息下，我覺得呢樣仲緊要過爭取民意，不幸中之大幸係冇人命事件，冇掂到公眾底線，雖然話觀感唔好，正如我所講要歸邊一早歸左，理解嘅始終都會理解，我唔覺得我地會失去太多輿論，反而班鬼會開始擔心自己安危，呢樣對我地有利！<br />\n<br />\n如果我係前線，返到屋企見到咁多咩失民意 輸左場運動，你覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">前線兄弟會點諗？呢場係一個團隊戰，共同打擊左敵人先再檢討，一有事就割係做乜？團結先係力量！</span>呢樣真係要學吓藍絲 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n歡迎大家入黎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3798717bb917abea20b339639c3045f397dadfe2","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83d361565d4233f17a0d93a02be0d79b06e13a69","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"推 2"},{"pid":"049d6fbb9ed2d71f89e3b37021e4725b03a33123","tid":1467282,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"大撚哂?<br />\n有錯都唔屌得?"},{"pid":"2a5a971400260de80ecdb682727bc3b2a25beedf","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"推 3"},{"pid":"612156bd4c3273dfbdd3aa5d2d80188768d1f7a3","tid":1467282,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"f0ed16e462abfb9bed501d198aeb6e9d41267c6c","tid":1467282,"uid":110507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:40.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]黑警舉真槍前因後果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/aecEADU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/aecEADU</a>"},{"pid":"a001ab432cb01a2ae8ae0ff8e500f66368983f6b","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"049d6fbb9ed2d71f89e3b37021e4725b03a33123","tid":1467282,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"大撚哂?<br />\n有錯都唔屌得?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"有錯要檢討，但唔好放棄隊友。 警犬出左問題有冇即刻割？冇，係因為要穩定軍心"},{"pid":"d2d47e526786a6ce455df1b0b58310eeafb38864","tid":1467282,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"踢佢 同保佢 已經睇到大家好唔團結"},{"pid":"0226029790469783dc2df3e264f4a3ff2d240191","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7f8ae00acf1602b866e395a8f3c85ae832d5289","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d47e526786a6ce455df1b0b58310eeafb38864","tid":1467282,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"踢佢 同保佢 已經睇到大家好唔團結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲敏感時候，更加應該團結左先，再慢慢檢討"},{"pid":"db4a054cd44fe9dd3fd118149bd2119d7649d89d","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07fdc63d6e18817d126e0774f370adfef74e7b43","tid":1467282,"uid":70897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"唔完美，可接受，可改善"},{"pid":"ab9877c4629cf15b48e205da847e33c537528842","tid":1467282,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"請手兄幫手推<br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 和理飛814<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a14d219e8d8151688b48598644e06e122bd74b3e","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07fdc63d6e18817d126e0774f370adfef74e7b43","tid":1467282,"uid":70897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"唔完美，可接受，可改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"冇任何事係完美，要做既係一齊努力去為完美而前進"},{"pid":"87e36d745f063b35325b17574bebdf4ace56cd74","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0d1f586c9b1326d80bcdffcd3147aa513eb4eec","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"0610573edb429ca804146a290ee4a52b7cbdce62","tid":1467282,"uid":273037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"打完又點，又無兄弟比人拉，又無手足受傷，點解要割？ 之前聽d和理非講，要散水要撒要be water. 手足被拉，絲打被爆眼，邊邊先係岩，自己識分析啦！"},{"pid":"b6bbc2c31a6fd482464682168a6ec5fd10869af0","tid":1467282,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"［中計撚入］唔好成日話輸民心啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b059ab62f2fb6de9320a5eb017c2f6bafc66d8a","tid":1467282,"uid":75338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"edd6d5f40a08d2ab7242f685a28e0332d7375fb3","tid":1467282,"uid":290774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049d6fbb9ed2d71f89e3b37021e4725b03a33123","tid":1467282,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"大撚哂?<br />\n有錯都唔屌得?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"唔好屌 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd017e6788a419300fe02b6dd0f4685f91f8dc7f","tid":1467282,"uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"遇鬼時<br />\n<br />\n1）先捉，<br />\n<br />\n2）圍大圈，分隔 同比多d 記者同人映隻鬼，<br />\n<br />\n個個企到密，根本映唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如鬼或自己人有受傷，都要拍片搵在場醫護幫忙<br />\n<br />\n自己傷固之然要醫護， 亦要係記者前問鬼有冇受傷或身體不適，搵在場醫護幫忙做初步檢查，盡番人道立場同道德高地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）搵記者影記錄，重點指出隻鬼做左乜野犯罪行為如打人，煽動，藏有危險品之類，所以採訪101拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n有物證就映埋物證。同令佢身分曝光，唔好祈望隻鬼會自爆，如果你諗住全世界鏡頭前嚴刑迫供，咁根本係另類送人頭，更何況打死隻鬼，相信佢都唔會講。<br />\n<br />\n闡明你嘅行為係合法性同正當性，同有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）同時搵議員，叫議員處理/議員報警處理。<br />\n相信10多其9都上白車，popo都放人。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，你留住隻鬼冇乜用，只會令現場仲難控制仲亂，好似今日咁，好易比其他鬼去分化，阻醫護阻記者，<br />\n<br />\n如只做1-4，我知大家可能會好嬲，想發洩，但係隻鬼重點係要佢曝光比世界，囉資料，囉更多頻譜，依個先更有利。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好忘記一舉一動既然係鏡頭前，就要有鏡頭禮儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有最好的方法，要有改善的辦法"},{"pid":"11890bd96b8f3f5db9ab80af28ea54e504bf24d3","tid":1467282,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f8ae00acf1602b866e395a8f3c85ae832d5289","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d47e526786a6ce455df1b0b58310eeafb38864","tid":1467282,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"踢佢 同保佢 已經睇到大家好唔團結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲敏感時候，更加應該團結左先，再慢慢檢討"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:58.000Z","msg":"我地要黎場debate 之後再決定要放生佢 或者其他"},{"pid":"e7cb8acc51e70507cc5eb92f2e25e18b612fd7fd","tid":1467282,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"前線辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係前線同埋冷靜可以共存的<br />\n<br />\n大家對唔對得住天琦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1cf3cd5466