地有利！<br />\n<br />\n如果我係前線，返到屋企見到咁多咩失民意 輸左場運動，你覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">前線兄弟會點諗？呢場係一個團隊戰，共同打擊左敵人先再檢討，一有事就割係做乜？團結先係力量！</span>呢樣真係要學吓藍絲 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n歡迎大家入黎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYNcbaE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYNcbaE.png&h=8aca2c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算係真係打仗<br />\n任何軍隊一定係紀律行頭<br />\n如果唔係一兩件on9係可以壞左大事<br />\n和理非回合就和理非到底<br />\n勇武環境就徹底勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"我認同，所以我哋要嘅你檢討並制定方案去改善日後嘅運動"},{"pid":"aa0b3bfe75c89845f5806aa18ea234cb97fdd759","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02b3290de7e8410291686b7f7996b43776bb2f13","tid":1467282,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:28.000Z","msg":"不完美<br />\n可接受<br />\n要改善<br />\n八一八"},{"pid":"a27c1caaecbbaffa75f31b9cb9f7d87ecab73ffb","tid":1467282,"uid":48889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"要團結<br />\n屌埋呢半個鐘好喇"},{"pid":"bd852369d2f14f5308df3e5929033f9c48d2503f","tid":1467282,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"「示威者在這兩個月來真是疲於奔命，很多休息時間都沒有，其實真是很辛苦。我們有時都要體諒，有時那一刻電光火石，影響判斷，有時出現誤中，都是不以為奇的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"bfd0f755de277a1f452a3a049ef9ccf8bd7e03aa","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8b8cdf2ef0fbcdbb21396516833cd2267d35a24f","tid":1467282,"uid":155584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"294694b8862851f97cff7df3dbde21fa56a206d9","tid":1467282,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:03.000Z","msg":"我係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句建議姐818<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"74e3e9cc0edf145a4bc931b969cd1c2ee77c0955","tid":1467282,"uid":215667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"呢單野... 除左陰謀論 我唔識拆<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割 <br />\n我尊重前線  但請注意前線應有的態度 <br />\n唔割 唔代表你可以拎出黎講<br />\n請前線手足要經常提醒左右果位 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陰謀論，可以推算到去811 果日 <br />\n究竟班狗潛藏左係武勇派入面咁多日<br />\n無啦啦點解會揀係果日現身？<br />\n<br />\n點解今日咁易比你捉到個公安<br />\n點解搞左個公安成5個鐘都冇狗黎救 <br />\n仲要圍住個公安咁耐有班要打要殺<br />\n有手足就阻止 但果班完全入唔到腦<br />\n相信好多人都見到<br />\n<br />\n之後無啦啦又比你捉多隻鬼<br />\n隻鬼唔認係記者 個袋又有件藍色衫 <br />\n（明引你入局）<br />\n你地班人見到藍衫果下仲唔著晒火 <br />\n（我都有...著）<br />\n但之後都有手足護住 雖然到最後都係混亂收場 <br />\n<br />\n我分析唔夠完整 <br />\n希望各位補完"},{"pid":"54e1157050ede60b8ee6948bd3d80d459996cf67","tid":1467282,"uid":270733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0